<h1>General Procedure and Requirements for Application Review</h1>
<p>The applicants for a Child Care Center, Family Child Care Home or Group Child Care Home shall apply for building permits. If construction work is to be part of the application construction drawings are to be attached for review. Applications shall have attached the applicants current license from the Office of Early Childhood or pending application form for licensure to the Office of Early Childhood.&nbsp;The application shall include the following information:&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
